description:
Alex Caselnes was an http://anidb.net/ch1535 [Alliance] vice admiral of logistics who served as a staff officer and close friend of Fleet Admiral http://anidb.net/ch737 [Yang Wenli]. Regarded as being an efficient bureaucrat, he was an expert in administrative and logistical work, essentially being the chief of logistics for the Yang Fleet and http://anidb.net/ch1762 [Iserlohn Fortress].
Source: Gineipaedia
name: Alex Caselnes
